[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/help_suit_game_try"]
[Student "S"]
{Partner is inviting you to bid game, and your 8 points are right in the "judgement" area.

But he has asked you to use judgement based on your \D holding, which is awful. So you sign off at 3\H. }

